cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper discusses machine learning and deep neural networks, which are commonly studied in the computer science sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also touches on the topic of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the analysis of the networks' performance under various distortions suggests a potential application in natural language processing (cs.CL).
